These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, february, art-decoing
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, chinese, french, polish
There 4 different types of food: peach, apple, grapes, nectarine
House: futuristic, art-deco, ranch-style, tower
1. the chinese is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the person eating grapes is the japanese##1
4. the person who's birthday is in art-decoing is on the right of the chinese##1
5. the french is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating apple##1
7. the chinese is the futuristic house##1
8. the person eating apple is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
9. the person who's birthday is in art-decoing is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | august  | art-decoing  | april | february |
| Nationality           | chinese | japanese | polish  | french  |
| Food   | nectarine       | grapes      | peach | apple      |
| House           | futuristic          | art-deco     | ranch-style    | tower     |

