.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, modern, futuristic
4 different pets are kept: dog, pony, frog, guinea-pig
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, green, fuchsia, azure
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, reading, singing, hiking
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes azure is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
6. the modern house is the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the art-deco house##1
8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House      | modern     | farmhouse       | art-deco | futuristic        |
| Pet          | guinea-pig     | pony       | frog   | dog   |
| Color   | fuchsia      | green       | azure     | purple    |
| Hobby         | singing | hiking | writing | reading |

