.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, folk, hip-hop, salsa
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite, begonia, dahlia
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, chess, magic-tricks, photography
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, emerald, red, yellow
 1. the fan of salsa is the person who likes yellow##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 5. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Music-Genre      | folk | d&b       | salsa        | hip-hop        |
| Flower           | aconite   | begonia | balloon-flower   | dahlia |
| Hobby   | cooking     | chess    | photography | magic-tricks        |
| Color           | red         | azure  | yellow       | emerald         |

