.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blood-red, fuchsia, black
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, craftsman, cape-cod
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, tram, boat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, december, march
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
8. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color           | blood-red   | chestnut  | black | fuchsia |
| House   | craftsman | cape-cod       | futuristic       | gothic-revival     |
| Transport   | tram       | boat    | jet-ski     | airplane  |
| Birthday           | june     | december | march     | july         |

