.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, lemonade, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, drawing, card-games, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, ebony, white, green
There 4 different types of food: tomato, radish, papaya, lime
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes green is on the right of the person eating lime##1
6. the person eating lime is the person who likes white##1
7. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage           | cola  | lemonade    | iced-tea | tea |
| Hobby   | card-games      | drawing    | hiking         | woodworking    |
| Color   | ebony   | red     | white          | green      |
| Food         | radish | tomato | lime      | papaya      |

