 7. the modern house is the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City    | colone | berlin     | hamburg    | nizza |
