7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the manager is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
