 4. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the game-smoker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 9. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
| Flower          | balloon-flower  | iris   | daisy       | tulip     |
