.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, chinchilla, goat
There 4 different types of food: spinach, zucchini, pineapple, orange
City: miami, san-francisco, hannover, nizza
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, orchid, begonia, dahlia
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
